message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "MATLAB Agentic Toolkit"
abstract: 
  The MATLAB® Agentic Toolkit allows you to use AI agents with MATLAB 
  by giving your AI agent the knowledge and context to work efficiently 
  with MATLAB and its toolboxes. Use this toolkit to provide trusted 
  MATLAB capabilities to your agent.

